Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.16,0:23:50.70,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}在記憶中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.85,0:23:56.17,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一直尋找着
