Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.48,0:24:12.14,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}即使軀體消亡
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.31,0:24:17.86,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}也一定跑到終點
